sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor NV as Nhan vien
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant Staff as Staff Service
    participant StaffDB as Staff DB

    Note over NV,StaffDB: Buoc 1 - Check-in bat dau ca lam

    NV->>GW: POST /api/staff/attendance/check-in
    Note over NV,GW: shiftId tuy chon, note tuy chon
    GW->>Staff: Forward request - yeu cau auth STAFF

    Staff->>StaffDB: employee.findByAccountId(accountId)
    StaffDB-->>Staff: employee record

    alt Nhan vien khong ton tai
        Staff-->>GW: 404 Not Found
        GW-->>NV: Nhan vien khong ton tai
    else Da check-in truoc do chua check-out
        Staff->>StaffDB: attendance.findOpenRecord(employeeId)
        StaffDB-->>Staff: attendance record chua check-out
        Staff-->>GW: 400 Bad Request
        GW-->>NV: Ban chua check-out ca truoc
    else Hop le
        Staff->>StaffDB: attendance.create
        Note over Staff,StaffDB: employeeId, shiftId tuy chon<br/>checkInTime=now, status=WORKING
        StaffDB-->>Staff: attendance record

        Staff-->>GW: 201 Created
        Note over Staff,GW: attendanceId, employeeId<br/>checkInTime, status=WORKING
        GW-->>NV: Check-in thanh cong
    end

    Note over NV,StaffDB: Buoc 2 - Check-out ket thuc ca lam

    NV->>GW: POST /api/staff/attendance/check-out
    Note over NV,GW: note tuy chon
    GW->>Staff: Forward request - yeu cau auth STAFF

    Staff->>StaffDB: attendance.findOpenRecord(employeeId)
    StaffDB-->>Staff: attendance record dang mo

    alt Chua check-in
        Staff-->>GW: 400 Bad Request
        GW-->>NV: Ban chua check-in
    else Hop le
        Staff->>Staff: workingHours = checkOutTime - checkInTime
        Staff->>StaffDB: attendance.update
        Note over Staff,StaffDB: checkOutTime=now<br/>workingHours, status=COMPLETED
        StaffDB-->>Staff: attendance da cap nhat

        Staff-->>GW: 200 OK
        Note over Staff,GW: attendanceId, checkInTime<br/>checkOutTime, workingHours
        GW-->>NV: Check-out thanh cong
    end

